<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us - PetCare</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/assets/Favicon.ico" type="image/jpeg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/contact.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/cb8535f973.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <a href="/index" class="logo"><i class="fa-solid fa-paw"></i>Pet<span>Care</span></a>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <a href="/index">Home</a>
            <a href="/services">Services</a>
            <a href="/about">About Us</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
            <a href="/auth/login">Login</a>
        </nav>
        <i id="menu-btn" class="fas fa-bars"></i>
    </header>

    <section class="contact">
        <h1 class="heading">Contact Us</h1>
        <div class="box-container">
            <div class="box">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-headphones"></i>
                <p class="center" style="font-size:1.7rem; color:var(--light-color);">People can Live Chat with our support</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Support</a>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <i class="fa-regular fa-envelope"></i>
                <p class="center" style="font-size:1.7rem; color:var(--light-color);">Use this Email to send us about the problem faced at <span style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:bold;">xyz@gmail.com</span></p>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>
                <p class="center" style="font-size:1.7rem; color:var(--light-color);">Toll Free Number: <span style="color:var(--green);font-weight:bold;">+1800 200 300 400</span></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="form">
        <h1 class="heading">Contact Us By Filling Form</h1>
        <div class="container" style="display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center;">
            <form action="/contact" method="POST" style="
                background: var(--white);
                border-radius: .5rem;
                box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
                border: var(--border);
                text-align: center;
                padding: 2rem;
                max-width: 450px;
                width: 100%;
                margin: 2rem auto;
                font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            ">
                <h3 style="
                    text-align: center;
                    padding-bottom: 2rem;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    color: var(--orange);
                    font-size: 2rem;
                    letter-spacing: .2rem;
                ">Fill Up This Form</h3>
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Enter Your Full Name" class="box" required style="
                    width: 100%;
                    margin: .7rem 0;
                    border-radius: .5rem;
                    border: var(--border);
                    font-size: 1.6rem;
                    color: var(--black);
                    padding: 1rem;
                ">
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter Your Email" class="box" required style="
                    width: 100%;
                    margin: .7rem 0;
                    border-radius: .5rem;
                    border: var(--border);
                    font-size: 1.6rem;
                    color: var(--black);
                    padding: 1rem;
                ">
                <textarea name="problem" placeholder="Write About Your Problem" class="box" required style="
                    width: 100%;
                    margin: .7rem 0;
                    border-radius: .5rem;
                    border: var(--border);
                    font-size: 1.6rem;
                    color: var(--black);
                    padding: 1rem;
                    min-height: 100px;
                    resize: vertical;
                "></textarea>
                <input type="submit" value="Send Us" class="btn" style="
                    background: var(--orange);
                    color: var(--white);
                    border: none;
                    border-radius: .5rem;
                    padding: .9rem 2.5rem;
                    font-size: 1.2rem;
                    font-weight: bold;
                    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
                    cursor: pointer;
                    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
                    transition: background 0.2s;
                "
                onmouseover="this.style.background='rgb(0, 128, 0)'"
                onmouseout="this.style.background='rgb(200, 132, 7)'"
                >
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- footer starts -->
    <section class="footer">
        <div class="footer-content">
           <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-paw"></i>Pet<span>Care</span></h3> 
           <p>PetCare is a pet caring shop, where we provide facilites and various useful treatments. We offer Massage, a good ground, expert staff, good facilites and much more! Visit us anytime :). We are closed only on Thursday and our regular timings are 9:00AM to 10:00PM.</p>
           <ul class="socials">
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fa-brands fa-google-plus-g"></i></a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-youtube"></i></a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square"></i></a></li>
         </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="footer-bottom">
       <p>copyright &copy;<span id="currentYear"></span> <a href="#">Shode Miracle</a> - Pet Care All rights reserved.</p>
    </section>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/cb8535f973.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
    <script>
      document.getElementById('currentYear').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    </script>
    <script> window.chtlConfig = { chatbotId: "5358877347" } </script>
    <script async data-id="5358877347" id="chtl-script" type="text/javascript" src="https://chatling.ai/js/embed.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
